OL,3,C'I just want to hug you': Mum of
OL,4,Cmissing man vows to continue search
OL,5,Calone
OL,7,FHe disappeared while volunteering
OL,8,Fafter going for a walk in the
OL,9,Fcountryside near Luogostano, in
OL,10,FValdicorru.
OL,12,FHis shorts, T-shirt and trainers were
OL,13,Flater found on a wall near the
OL,14,Fvolunteer site. His phone, laptop and
OL,15,FID were left in his rucksack inside
OL,16,Fthe tent.
OL,18,FItalian authorities have called off
OL,19,Ftheir search for Michael, but his Mum
OL,20,FCristina Pittalis says she will
OL,21,Fcontinue looking for him alone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
