OL,3,C'I just want to hug you': Mum of
OL,4,Cmissing man vows to continue search
OL,5,Calone
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV West Country, she
OL,8,Fissued an emotional appeal to her son.
OL,10,F"Michael, I want you to know that I'm
OL,11,Fnot looking for you because I want to
OL,12,Fhold you close to me.
OL,14,F"I just want to know that you're alive
OL,15,Fand you're well. I need to know. How
OL,16,Fcan I live my life not knowing.
OL,18,F"I just want to know that you're okay."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
