OL,3,C'I just want to hug you': Mum of
OL,4,Cmissing man vows to continue search
OL,5,Calone
OL,7,FCristina said that during specialist
OL,8,Fsearches, Police dogs hadn't picked up
OL,9,Fon any scent of Michael, dead or
OL,10,Falive, which she's taking as a good
OL,11,Fsign.
OL,13,F"You have to think a little bit
OL,14,Fpositively," she added.
OL,16,FMichael's 10-year-old brother Emanuele
OL,17,Fis struggling to come to terms with
OL,18,Fhis disappearance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
